snippet.title: Super FUNNY CHIHUAHUAS - It's TIME to LAUGH HARD!
snippet.description:
Chihuahuas are so super funny dogs! They just never fail to make us laugh super hard! Chihuahua videos are the best entertainment! Look how all these chihuahuas fail, make funny sounds, play, sleep,... So super funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
